  		<div class="text">
  
   
    	<p><strong>The general and breast surgeon:</strong></p>


<p>General surgeons can operate on a range of problems in an emergency.  
<p>Their emergency service is known as “on call”</p>
<p>Breast surgeons specialise in treating diseases of the breast in men and women. Some will be cancerous whilst others are harmless. </p> 
<p>They work in teams with nurses, radiologists and radiographers to deliver a ‘one stop shop’ to their patients.</p>

		
    	
  		
